DATASET LICENCE NOTICE

The Financial PhraseBank dataset (Malo et al., 2014) used in this project is
licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 3.0
(CC BY-NC-SA 3.0). It is NOT included in this repository. It must be
downloaded independently from:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ankurzing/sentiment-analysis-for-financial-news

The Reuters, CNBC, and Guardian headline datasets used for cross-dataset
validation are available under Kaggle open access terms at:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/notlucasp/financial-news-headlines

The FinBERT model (ProsusAI/finbert) is hosted on HuggingFace Hub under its
own licence. See: https://huggingface.co/ProsusAI/finbert
